# XavierAI Organization Code Owners
# 
# This file defines who has review rights for different parts of the codebase.
# Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more owners.
# 
# Order is important; the last matching pattern takes the most precedence.
# When someone opens a pull request that only modifies files matching a 
# pattern, only the owner(s) of that pattern will be requested for review.

# Global fallback - these users/teams are requested if no other rules match
* @xavieraiorg/tech-leads

